---
title: Buffalo Pork Belly & Cheesy Moemoe Potato Wedges with Charred Corn Slaw & Onion Rings
description: This week's special ingreadient is Moemoe Potato - a variety unique to New Zealand, Moemoe potatoes are known for their creamy flesh with streaks of purple. Their smooth texture and delicate, earthy flavours make them perfect for roasting or boiling. Try them in tonight’s dish for a delicious and vibrant twist!
